overview: July 9th is the second night of the World Series Wrestling Phoenix Rising Tour straight from Melbourne, Australia.  The event will feature international pro wrestling stars such as Matt Cardona, Johnny Superstar, Buddy Matthews and Brian Cage, Jon Gresham, Alex Zayne, Joey Janela, Trey Miguel, Flip Gordon, Taya Valkyrie, Chelsea Green and Tenille Dashwood, plus Australia's top pro wrestling stars!  Get Ready for the Ride of Your Life!
title: World Series Wrestling: Phoenix Rising (Night 2)
